* Set up command line args
	-p <path_to_neuvoo_overlay>
	-d <device>
	-f <features1:feature2:feature3:...>
	-c <create overlay links>
	-s <save to /etc/make.profile.neuvoo/parent>

* Autodetection
	1. Automatically parse /etc/make.conf for PORTDIR_OVERLAY and check
	2. Automatically parse /etc/make.conf for layman and check
	3. Automatically check passed -p and check

* Arrays
	1. Automatically generate device list
	2. Automatically generate features list
